metadata.content:
# Droopy McCool - Behind the scenes[]

Droopy McCool was portrayed by Deep Roy, uncredited, in Return of the Jedi. New footage of McCool was filmed for the Special Edition of Return of the Jedi, but it is unclear if it was Deep Roy again.

The character was referred to as "Der Droopy" in some early material, including a Return of the Jedi coloring book, and unused molds for Pepperidge Farm's Star Wars cookies from 1983.
